-It's in New York.

8
00:00:17.935 --> 00:00:19.437
I've done the most terrible thing.

9
00:00:20.271 --> 00:00:22.356
Aah!

10
00:00:22.440 --> 00:00:23.691
Redback's alive.

11
00:00:23.774 --> 00:00:25.234
<i>She's alive!</i>

12
00:00:26.277 --> 00:00:27.319
No.

13
00:00:27.403 --> 00:00:30.573
[Director] <i>I would caution you against</i>
<i>what you're planning to do next.</i>

14
00:00:30.656 --> 00:00:32.324
[Queenie] <i>Well. I don't care</i>

15
00:00:32.408 --> 00:00:34.034
what you caution.

16
00:00:34.118 --> 00:00:35.286
<i>because I'm gonna kill her.</i>

17
00:00:35.369 --> 00:00:36.829
